<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Privacy Policy - Task Manager</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>


<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-100 text-gray-900 min-h-screen font-sans flex flex-col">

  <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="flex-grow container mx-auto px-6 py-12">
      <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-10 border border-gray-200">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 border-b border-gray-300 pb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

        <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
          Welcome to Task Manager! Your privacy is important to us. This privacy policy explains how we handle your
          data.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-700 mt-6 mb-2">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <li>Personal info (name, email) for account creation</li>
          <li>Tasks and Subtasks data entered by you</li>
          <li>Cookies for login session and preferences</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-700 mt-6 mb-2">2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
          We use your data to provide a secure, personalized experience. Your data is never shared with third parties
          without your consent.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-700 mt-6 mb-2">3. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
          You can update or delete your data anytime through your account settings or by contacting support.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-700 mt-6 mb-2">4. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
          We use encryption, secure authentication, and session-based JWT protection to ensure your data is safe.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-indigo-700 mt-6 mb-2">5. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          If you have any questions about your privacy, email us at
          <a href="mailto:support@taskmanager.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">support@taskmanager.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer Partial -->
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>